title: Watch: Cowboys DE Jeremy Mincey releases music video, song focusing on his recent wedding
text:
Dallas Cowboys defensive end Jeremy Mincey missed some time earlier this season with a concussion, so his on-the-field production has been limited.
Off the field, though, he continues to produce.
Music videos, that is.
Mincey, who raps under the name "Mr. Mince," recently released a music video of his song "Just Work," which features shots of he and his wife, Markevia, spliced with footage from their wedding. It's the second video released on Youtube under Mincey's account, Mr Mince Productions Inc.
The first was "Cowboys Anthem." The Minceys married in June.
Give it a listen and a watch and let us know what you think:
